    "There he struck a friendship with a young Columbia University medieval art history student, <a href=\"/schapirer\">Meyer Schapiro</a>, offering Schapiro to study under him.": [],
    "In 1927 he received an honorary doctor of letters degree from the University of Marburg.": [
